Lde/ecspride/LocationLeak2;->onLocationC: This method receives a Location object and extracts its latitude and longitude as strings, storing them in the LocationLeak2 object's latitude and longtitude fields.
Lde/ecspride/LocationLeak2;->onResume:(): This method receives a Location object and extracts its latitude and longitude as strings, storing them in the LocationLeak2 object's latitude and longtitude fields. It then displays these values as Toast messages.
